trans-unit.source: Contains information that enables a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Binding" /> to resolve a data binding to either the property of an object or the property of the current object in a list of objects.
trans-unit.target: Contiene información que permite que <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Binding" /> resuelva un enlace a datos en la propiedad de un objeto o en la propiedad del objeto actual en una lista de objetos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> is returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.BindingMemberInfo%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> class.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> devuelto por la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding.BindingMemberInfo%2A> propiedad de la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> clase.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> is created from the string passed to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> se crea a partir de la cadena pasada a la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor.

trans-unit.source: The following code example prints the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> for each control on a form.
trans-unit.target: El siguiente código de ejemplo imprime la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> para cada control en un formulario.

trans-unit.source: A navigation path that resolves to either the property of an object or the property of the current object in a list of objects.
trans-unit.target: Ruta de navegación que resuelve la propiedad de un objeto o la propiedad del objeto actual en una lista de objetos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> is created automatically when you call the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor with a control-property name, data source, and navigation path.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> se crea automáticamente cuando se llama a la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor con un nombre de propiedad de control, el origen de datos y la ruta de navegación.

trans-unit.source: The `dataMember` parameter contains the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> string.
trans-unit.target: El `dataMember` parámetro contiene el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> cadena.

trans-unit.source: Gets the property name of the data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el nombre de propiedad del objeto enlazado a datos.

trans-unit.source: The property name of the data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: El nombre de propiedad del objeto enlazado a datos.

trans-unit.source: This can be an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Puede ser una cadena vacía ("").

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> is the last item found in the navigation path returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> es el último elemento que se encuentra en la ruta de navegación devuelta por la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: For example, if a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> is created that has a `dataMember` parameter of "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> will return "OrderDate".
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, si un nuevo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> se crea que tiene un `dataMember` parámetro de "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> devolverá "OrderDate".

trans-unit.source: The following code example gets the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> of each <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> on a form, and prints the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property values of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.
trans-unit.target: El código siguiente en el ejemplo se obtiene la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> de cada <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> en un formulario y se imprime el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, y <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> valores de propiedad de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the information that is used to specify the property name of the data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la información que se utiliza para especificar el nombre de propiedad del objeto enlazado a datos.

trans-unit.source: An empty string (""), a single property name, or a hierarchy of period-delimited property names that resolves to the property name of the final data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: Una cadena vacía (""), un único nombre de propiedad o una jerarquía de nombres de propiedad delimitados por puntos que resuelve el nombre de propiedad del objeto final enlazado a datos.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> is created automatically when you call the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor with a control-property name, data source, and navigation path.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> se crea automáticamente cuando se llama a la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.%23ctor%2A> constructor con un nombre de propiedad de control, el origen de datos y la ruta de navegación.

trans-unit.source: The `dataMember` parameter contains the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> string.
trans-unit.target: El `dataMember` parámetro contiene el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> cadena.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> is the period delimitated combination of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> values.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> es la combinación delimitada por puntos períoda de la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> y <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> valores.

trans-unit.source: For example, when a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> is created by using a `dataMember` parameter of "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> will return "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate".
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, cuando un nuevo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> se crea mediante un `dataMember` parámetro de "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> devolverá "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate".

trans-unit.source: The following code example gets the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> object of each <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> on a form, and prints the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property values of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.
trans-unit.target: El código siguiente en el ejemplo se obtiene la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> objeto de cada <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> en un formulario y se imprime el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, y <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> valores de propiedad de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the property name, or the period-delimited hierarchy of property names, that comes before the property name of the data-bound object.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el nombre de propiedad, o la jerarquía de nombres de propiedad delimitados por puntos, que precede al nombre de propiedad del objeto enlazado a datos.

trans-unit.source: The property name, or the period-delimited hierarchy of property names, that comes before the data-bound object property name.
trans-unit.target: El nombre de propiedad, o la jerarquía de nombres de propiedad delimitados por puntos, que precede al nombre de propiedad del objeto enlazado a datos.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> is the period delimitated combination of property names that comes before the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> in the navigational path returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> es el período de combinación delimitada por puntos de propiedad nombres que viene antes que la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A> en la ruta de navegación devuelta por la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: For example, when a new <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> is created that has a `dataMember` parameter of "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> will return "Customers.custToOrders".
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, cuando un nuevo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> se crea que tiene un `dataMember` parámetro de "Customers.custToOrders.OrderDate", <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A> devolverá "Customers.custToOrders".

trans-unit.source: The following code example gets the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> of each <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> on a form, and prints the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> property values of <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.
trans-unit.target: El código siguiente en el ejemplo se obtiene la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo> de cada <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Binding> en un formulario y se imprime el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingPath%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingField%2A>, y <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> valores de propiedad de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo>.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare for equality.
trans-unit.target: El objeto cuya igualdad se va a comparar.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified object is equal to this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" />.
trans-unit.target: Determina si el objeto especificado es igual a este <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="otherObject" /> is a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" /> and both <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember" /> strings are equal; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si <paramref name="otherObject" /> es un <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" /> y ambas cadenas <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember" /> son iguales; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> strings are compared with a culture setting of <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember%2A> se comparan las cadenas con una configuración de referencia cultural <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture%2A>.

trans-unit.target: Devuelve el código hash de este objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" />.

trans-unit.target: Código hash de esta <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" />.

trans-unit.target: Determina si los dos objetos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo" /> son iguales.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember" /> strings for <paramref name="a" /> and <paramref name="b" /> are equal; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si las cadenas de <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.BindingMemberInfo.BindingMember" /> para <paramref name="a" /> y <paramref name="b" /> son iguales; de lo contrario, es <see langword="false" />.
